item.title: Silver 01 - Meet Mr. Pokemon!
item.description:
Silver 01 - Meet Mr. Pokemon!
With the highly-anticipated release of HeartGold and SoulSilver in Japan in September, more and more Pokemon fans are getting psyched up for the games. So why not take a stroll down memory lane and watch some of the highlights from the original games, Gold and Silver. This is Marriland's Silver Adventure! In this episode, I get my Pokemon from Professor Elm, stop by Cherrygrove City, and get my Pokedex from Professor Oak! I'll be posting Silver videos over the next week or two as well as tweeting about my playthrough as I play on my Twitter feed: - http://www.twitter.com/Marriland I'll also be posting tons of HeartGold and SoulSilver stuff both there (you might not want to follow me if you don't want spoilers!) and on my website as the games are released: - http://pokemon.marriland.com One last thing: these Silver videos are not meant to be a "follow me through EVERYTHING" style video like Diamond and Yellow are. They're going to be cut and condensed to show you the most memorable moments and stuff you should know for HeartGold and SoulSilver. However, a lot of that is because I'll be covering in even more depths HeartGold and SoulSilver (more akin to my Platinum US videos or even Yellow, depending on how much I can talk during the Japanese text), so I don't want to be too repetitive. Enjoy the videos!
